# Phase 1 — Core Annotations & Base Classes

## Context
This phase implements the foundational types for the authorization library in `point-my-auth-core`.

## Files to Create

### 1. `@AuthorizeEntity` annotation
- **Path**: `point-my-auth-core/src/main/java/com/pointmyauth/annotation/AuthorizeEntity.java`
- **Package**: `com.pointmyauth.annotation`
- **Fields**: `ids()`, `includeUser()`, `includeAuthorizationCase()`, `authorizationCase()`, `authorizationHandler()`
- **Meta**: `@Target(ElementType.METHOD)`, `@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)`, `@Documented`

### 2. `AuthorizationHandler<U>` interface
- **Path**: `point-my-auth-core/src/main/java/com/pointmyauth/handler/AuthorizationHandler.java`
- **Package**: `com.pointmyauth.handler`
- **Method**: `void authorize(AuthorizationContext<U> context)`
- **Javadoc**: Describe the contract with `@param <U>` type param

### 3. `AuthorizationContext<U>` — immutable context
- **Path**: `point-my-auth-core/src/main/java/com/pointmyauth/context/AuthorizationContext.java`
- **Fields**: `resolvedIds` (Map), `currentUser` (U, nullable), `authorizationCase` (String), `interceptedMethod` (Method)
- **Builder**: Static Builder class
- **Helper methods**: `getId(String, Class<T>)`, `getLongId(String)`, `getStringId(String)`

### 4. `CurrentUserProvider<U>` — functional interface
- **Path**: `point-my-auth-core/src/main/java/com/pointmyauth/user/CurrentUserProvider.java`
- **Package**: `com.pointmyauth.user`
- **Annotation**: `@FunctionalInterface`
- **Method**: `U getCurrentUser()`

### 5. `AuthorizationException` — runtime exception
- **Path**: `point-my-auth-core/src/main/java/com/pointmyauth/exception/AuthorizationException.java`
- **Package**: `com.pointmyauth.exception`
- **Extends**: `RuntimeException`
- **Constructors**: (String message), (String message, Throwable cause)

## Conventions
- Javadoc in English on all public API
- Nullability annotations: `@Nullable`, `@NonNull` from `jakarta.annotation`
- No Spring-specific imports in these base classes

## Verification
```bash
mvn compile -pl point-my-auth-core -DskipTests
```
